---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Worldwide Chemical Shipping & Logistics" description="Global shipping for industrial chemicals from Germany. Hazmat-certified transport, secure packaging & international delivery for all UE Chemicals products." activePage="shipping">

  <!-- ========== HERO ========== -->
  <section class="sh-hero">
    <div class="sh-hero-bg">
      <img src="/images/industrial-worker-holding-plastic-cans-with-chemicals-production-plant.jpg" alt="Global chemical shipping from Essen, Germany" />
      <div class="sh-hero-overlay"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container sh-hero-inner">
      <div class="sh-hero-content">
        <div class="sh-hero-badge"><i class="fas fa-truck-fast"></i> Global Logistics</div>
        <h1>Worldwide Chemical<br />Shipping &amp; Logistics</h1>
        <p class="sh-hero-sub">Safe, compliant international delivery of hazardous chemical products with full documentation, insurance, and real-time tracking.</p>
        <div class="sh-hero-actions">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-accent">Get Shipping Quote <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
          <a href="/ordering" class="btn btn-outline-white">Ordering Info <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="sh-hero-stats">
        <div class="sh-hero-stat">
          <span class="sh-hero-stat-num">6</span>
          <span class="sh-hero-stat-label">Continents Served</span>
        </div>
        <div class="sh-hero-stat">
          <span class="sh-hero-stat-num">100%</span>
          <span class="sh-hero-stat-label">Shipments Insured</span>
        </div>
        <div class="sh-hero-stat">
          <span class="sh-hero-stat-num">24h</span>
          <span class="sh-hero-stat-label">Quote Response</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== OVERVIEW ========== -->
  <section class="sh-overview">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="sh-overview-intro">
        <div class="section-label">Why Ship With Us</div>
        <h2>Safe &amp; Compliant Delivery Worldwide</h2>
        <p>UE Chemicals ships from our facility in Essen, Germany to destinations across all continents. Every shipment is handled by licensed hazardous materials carriers with full regulatory compliance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sh-overview-grid">
        <div class="sh-overview-card">
          <div class="sh-overview-icon"><i class="fas fa-earth-europe"></i></div>
          <h4>Global Coverage</h4>
          <p>We ship to Europe, Asia, Africa, North &amp; South America, and Oceania via licensed carriers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sh-overview-card">
          <div class="sh-overview-icon"><i class="fas fa-shield-halved"></i></div>
          <h4>Fully Insured</h4>
          <p>All shipments are insured against loss and damage during transit for complete peace of mind.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sh-overview-card">
          <div class="sh-overview-icon"><i class="fas fa-file-certificate"></i></div>
          <h4>Full Documentation</h4>
          <p>SDS, TDS, COA, customs declarations, and transport documents included with every shipment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sh-overview-card">
          <div class="sh-overview-icon"><i class="fas fa-box-open"></i></div>
          <h4>UN-Approved Packaging</h4>
          <p>Products shipped in UN-specification containers with proper hazmat labeling and tamper-proof sealing.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== TRANSPORT REGULATIONS ========== -->
  <section class="sh-regs">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:50px;">
        <div class="section-label">Compliance</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Transport Regulations</h2>
        <p style="max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;color:var(--body-text);">All shipments comply with international hazardous goods transport frameworks for maximum safety.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sh-regs-grid">
        <div class="sh-reg-card">
          <div class="sh-reg-header">
            <div class="sh-reg-icon"><i class="fas fa-truck"></i></div>
            <div>
              <h4>Road Transport</h4>
              <span class="sh-reg-code">ADR</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>European Agreement concerning the International Carriage of Dangerous Goods by Road.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Licensed hazmat carrier transport</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Driver ADR certification</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Emergency Instructions in Writing (EIW)</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Proper segregation protocols</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="sh-reg-card">
          <div class="sh-reg-header">
            <div class="sh-reg-icon"><i class="fas fa-ship"></i></div>
            <div>
              <h4>Sea Freight</h4>
              <span class="sh-reg-code">IMDG Code</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>International Maritime Dangerous Goods Code for ocean shipments.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> IMDG Class 8 &amp; 6.1 classification</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Marine pollutant labeling</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Container segregation compliance</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> UN-specification packaging</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="sh-reg-card">
          <div class="sh-reg-header">
            <div class="sh-reg-icon"><i class="fas fa-plane"></i></div>
            <div>
              <h4>Air Freight</h4>
              <span class="sh-reg-code">IATA DGR</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>International Air Transport Association Dangerous Goods Regulations.</p>
          <ul>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Cargo-only aircraft transport</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> UN certified leak-proof packaging</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Shipper's Declaration for DG</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Full IATA hazmat compliance</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== PACKAGING ========== -->
  <section class="sh-packaging">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="sh-pack-grid">
        <div class="sh-pack-content">
          <div class="section-label">Packaging</div>
          <h2>UN-Approved Packaging Standards</h2>
          <p>All chemical products are packaged in UN-specification containers rated for hazardous materials transport, ensuring product integrity and safety throughout the entire logistics chain.</p>
          <div class="sh-pack-items">
            <div class="sh-pack-item">
              <div class="sh-pack-item-icon"><i class="fas fa-flask"></i></div>
              <div>
                <strong>Steel Flasks</strong>
                <p>Standard 34.5 kg / 76 lbs UN-approved steel flasks for mercury products. Sealed and pressure-tested.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="sh-pack-item">
              <div class="sh-pack-item-icon"><i class="fas fa-bottle-droplet"></i></div>
              <div>
                <strong>HDPE Containers</strong>
                <p>High-density polyethylene bottles in steel drums with absorbent cushioning for oxidizers.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="sh-pack-item">
              <div class="sh-pack-item-icon"><i class="fas fa-tags"></i></div>
              <div>
                <strong>Hazmat Labeling</strong>
                <p>Every package labeled with UN number, proper shipping name, hazard class, and packing group.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="sh-pack-item">
              <div class="sh-pack-item-icon"><i class="fas fa-lock"></i></div>
              <div>
                <strong>Tamper-Proof Sealing</strong>
                <p>Sealed containers with tamper-evident closures and security indicators for maximum protection.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sh-pack-labels-card">
          <h4><i class="fas fa-triangle-exclamation"></i> Required Labels &amp; Markings</h4>
          <div class="sh-label-grid">
            <div class="sh-label"><i class="fas fa-skull-crossbones"></i><span>Toxic (Class 6.1)</span></div>
            <div class="sh-label"><i class="fas fa-flask-vial"></i><span>Corrosive (Class 8)</span></div>
            <div class="sh-label"><i class="fas fa-leaf"></i><span>Marine Pollutant</span></div>
            <div class="sh-label"><i class="fas fa-temperature-high"></i><span>Keep from Heat</span></div>
            <div class="sh-label"><i class="fas fa-hand"></i><span>Handle with Care</span></div>
            <div class="sh-label"><i class="fas fa-barcode"></i><span>UN Number</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== DELIVERY TIMELINE ========== -->
  <section class="sh-timeline">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:50px;">
        <div class="section-label">Delivery Timelines</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Estimated Shipping Times</h2>
        <p style="max-width:600px;margin:0 auto;color:var(--body-text);">From our warehouse in Essen, Germany to your destination.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sh-timeline-wrap">
        <div class="sh-timeline-cards">
          <div class="sh-tl-card">
            <div class="sh-tl-flag"><i class="fas fa-flag"></i></div>
            <h4>Germany</h4>
            <span class="sh-tl-method">Road (ADR)</span>
            <div class="sh-tl-days">1–3 <small>business days</small></div>
          </div>
          <div class="sh-tl-card">
            <div class="sh-tl-flag"><i class="fas fa-flag"></i></div>
            <h4>EU Countries</h4>
            <span class="sh-tl-method">Road / Sea</span>
            <div class="sh-tl-days">3–7 <small>business days</small></div>
          </div>
          <div class="sh-tl-card">
            <div class="sh-tl-flag"><i class="fas fa-flag"></i></div>
            <h4>United Kingdom</h4>
            <span class="sh-tl-method">Sea / Air</span>
            <div class="sh-tl-days">5–10 <small>business days</small></div>
          </div>
          <div class="sh-tl-card">
            <div class="sh-tl-flag"><i class="fas fa-flag"></i></div>
            <h4>North America</h4>
            <span class="sh-tl-method">Sea / Air</span>
            <div class="sh-tl-days">7–14 <small>business days</small></div>
          </div>
          <div class="sh-tl-card">
            <div class="sh-tl-flag"><i class="fas fa-flag"></i></div>
            <h4>South America</h4>
            <span class="sh-tl-method">Sea / Air</span>
            <div class="sh-tl-days">10–18 <small>business days</small></div>
          </div>
          <div class="sh-tl-card">
            <div class="sh-tl-flag"><i class="fas fa-flag"></i></div>
            <h4>Asia &amp; Middle East</h4>
            <span class="sh-tl-method">Sea / Air</span>
            <div class="sh-tl-days">10–21 <small>business days</small></div>
          </div>
          <div class="sh-tl-card">
            <div class="sh-tl-flag"><i class="fas fa-flag"></i></div>
            <h4>Africa</h4>
            <span class="sh-tl-method">Sea / Air</span>
            <div class="sh-tl-days">14–25 <small>business days</small></div>
          </div>
          <div class="sh-tl-card">
            <div class="sh-tl-flag"><i class="fas fa-flag"></i></div>
            <h4>Oceania</h4>
            <span class="sh-tl-method">Sea / Air</span>
            <div class="sh-tl-days">14–25 <small>business days</small></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="sh-tl-note">
          <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
          <p>Delivery times are estimates and may vary due to customs processing, destination regulations, and carrier schedules. Real-time tracking is provided for all shipments.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== PROCESS ========== -->
  <section class="sh-process">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center" style="margin-bottom:50px;">
        <div class="section-label">Simple Process</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">How Shipping Works</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="sh-steps">
        <div class="sh-step">
          <div class="sh-step-num">01</div>
          <div class="sh-step-line"></div>
          <h4>Request a Quote</h4>
          <p>Submit your product inquiry via our contact form or email. Include product, quantity, and destination.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sh-step">
          <div class="sh-step-num">02</div>
          <div class="sh-step-line"></div>
          <h4>Receive Proforma Invoice</h4>
          <p>We'll send a detailed invoice with pricing, shipping costs, payment details, and delivery timeline.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sh-step">
          <div class="sh-step-num">03</div>
          <div class="sh-step-line"></div>
          <h4>Confirm Payment</h4>
          <p>Complete payment via bank wire or cryptocurrency. Orders processed within 1–3 business days.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="sh-step">
          <div class="sh-step-num">04</div>
          <h4>Track Your Shipment</h4>
          <p>Receive tracking details and monitor your shipment from our warehouse to your doorstep.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ========== CTA ========== -->
  <section class="sh-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="sh-cta-inner">
        <h2>Ready to Ship? Get a Quote Today</h2>
        <p>Contact us with your product, quantity, and destination for a detailed shipping quote including costs, timelines, and documentation requirements.</p>
        <div class="sh-cta-actions">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-white">Request Shipping Quote <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
          <a href="mailto:info@useful-chemicals.com" class="btn btn-outline-white">Email Us <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ===== Hero ===== */
  .sh-hero { position: relative; min-height: 55vh; display: flex; align-items: center; }
  .sh-hero-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: 0; }
  .sh-hero-bg img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
  .sh-hero-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(10,15,30,.9), rgba(10,15,30,.65)); }
  .sh-hero-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; padding: 110px 0 60px; }
  .sh-hero-content { max-width: 650px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .sh-hero-badge { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.08); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12); backdrop-filter: blur(8px); padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 100px; font-size: .85rem; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 600; }
  .sh-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem); font-weight: 800; color: var(--white); line-height: 1.12; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .sh-hero-sub { color: rgba(255,255,255,.7); font-size: 1.08rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .sh-hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .sh-hero-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 16px; max-width: 500px; }
  .sh-hero-stat { background: rgba(255,255,255,.06); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1); backdrop-filter: blur(8px); padding: 18px 20px; border-radius: 12px; text-align: center; }
  .sh-hero-stat-num { display: block; font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--white); }
  .sh-hero-stat-label { font-size: .75rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .8px; font-weight: 600; }

  /* ===== Overview ===== */
  .sh-overview { padding: 90px 0; }
  .sh-overview-intro { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto 50px; text-align: center; }
  .sh-overview-intro h2 { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .sh-overview-intro p { color: var(--body-text); line-height: 1.8; }
  .sh-overview-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 24px; }
  .sh-overview-card { text-align: center; padding: 32px 24px; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; transition: all .3s; }
  .sh-overview-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.06); }
  .sh-overview-icon { width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 14px; background: rgba(252,82,32,.08); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.3rem; color: var(--accent); margin: 0 auto 16px; }
  .sh-overview-card h4 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .sh-overview-card p { color: var(--body-text); font-size: .9rem; line-height: 1.65; margin: 0; }

  /* ===== Regulations ===== */
  .sh-regs { padding: 90px 0; background: var(--light-bg); }
  .sh-regs-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 28px; }
  .sh-reg-card { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px 28px; transition: all .3s; }
  .sh-reg-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.06); }
  .sh-reg-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .sh-reg-icon { width: 50px; height: 50px; border-radius: 12px; background: var(--near-black); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: var(--white); font-size: 1.2rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .sh-reg-header h4 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .sh-reg-code { font-size: .78rem; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .5px; }
  .sh-reg-card > p { color: var(--body-text); font-size: .9rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .sh-reg-card ul { list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  .sh-reg-card li { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; padding: 8px 0; font-size: .9rem; color: var(--body-text); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .sh-reg-card li:first-child { border-top: none; }
  .sh-reg-card li i { color: var(--accent); font-size: .75rem; }

  /* ===== Packaging ===== */
  .sh-packaging { padding: 90px 0; }
  .sh-pack-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.3fr .7fr; gap: 50px; align-items: start; }
  .sh-pack-content h2 { font-size: 1.7rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .sh-pack-content > p { color: var(--body-text); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 30px; }
  .sh-pack-items { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }
  .sh-pack-item { display: flex; gap: 16px; }
  .sh-pack-item-icon { width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 10px; background: rgba(252,82,32,.08); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: var(--accent); font-size: 1rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .sh-pack-item strong { display: block; font-size: .95rem; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .sh-pack-item p { color: var(--body-text); font-size: .88rem; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }

  /* Labels card */
  .sh-pack-labels-card { background: var(--near-black); border-radius: 20px; padding: 36px 30px; }
  .sh-pack-labels-card > h4 { color: var(--white); font-size: 1rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .sh-pack-labels-card > h4 i { color: var(--accent); }
  .sh-label-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; }
  .sh-label { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; background: rgba(255,255,255,.07); padding: 14px 16px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08); }
  .sh-label i { color: var(--accent); font-size: 1.1rem; width: 22px; text-align: center; }
  .sh-label span { color: rgba(255,255,255,.85); font-size: .88rem; font-weight: 500; }

  /* ===== Timeline ===== */
  .sh-timeline { padding: 90px 0; background: var(--light-bg); }
  .sh-timeline-cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 18px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .sh-tl-card { background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; padding: 24px 20px; text-align: center; transition: all .3s; }
  .sh-tl-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-3px); }
  .sh-tl-flag { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .sh-tl-card h4 { font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .sh-tl-method { font-size: .78rem; color: var(--body-text); opacity: .6; display: block; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .sh-tl-days { font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--near-black); }
  .sh-tl-days small { font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--body-text); display: block; }
  .sh-tl-note { display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start; background: var(--white); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px 20px; }
  .sh-tl-note i { color: var(--accent); margin-top: 3px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .sh-tl-note p { color: var(--body-text); font-size: .88rem; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }

  /* ===== Process ===== */
  .sh-process { padding: 90px 0; }
  .sh-steps { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 0; }
  .sh-step { text-align: center; padding: 30px 24px; position: relative; }
  .sh-step-num { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .sh-step-line { position: absolute; top: 42px; right: -10px; width: 20px; height: 2px; background: var(--border); }
  .sh-step:last-child .sh-step-line { display: none; }
  .sh-step h4 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .sh-step p { color: var(--body-text); font-size: .88rem; line-height: 1.65; }

  /* ===== CTA ===== */
  .sh-cta { padding: 90px 0; }
  .sh-cta-inner { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--near-black), #1a1f2e); padding: 60px; border-radius: 24px; text-align: center; }
  .sh-cta-inner h2 { color: var(--white); font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .sh-cta-inner p { color: rgba(255,255,255,.7); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 30px; line-height: 1.7; }
  .sh-cta-actions { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  /* ===== Responsive ===== */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .sh-overview-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .sh-regs-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .sh-pack-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .sh-timeline-cards { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .sh-steps { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .sh-step-line { display: none; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .sh-overview-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .sh-hero-stats { grid-template-columns: 1fr; max-width: 100%; }
    .sh-timeline-cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .sh-steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .sh-label-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .sh-cta-inner { padding: 40px 24px; }
  }
</style>
